## ML-only script changes

After `git pull`, run with `.venv/bin/python` — no docker rebuild unless dependencies changed.

## Do not SCP

`gcloud compute scp` is only for **non-git artifacts** (data files, one-off logs) or emergencies when git is broken. Never SCP Python/JS source that belongs in the repo.

## Env / config on runtime

Use `ops/gcp/patch_playbook_v1_env.sh` (or edit `.env.compose`) on the VM **after** pull, then rebuild/recreate affected services.
